{"tid":904358,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶賊特製袋偷遍20市UNIQLO","createTime":"2018-11-16T09:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T12:40:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bfadea5a6c817820b1c2f1f5cdd9610c6fbc76dc","tid":904358,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:35:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181116/20547202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547202&d=cr7RxwK%2BUU964Ylf8DQEzTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=ec737029\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547202&h=777e26f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181116/20547202</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月16日 <br />\n<br />\n情侶賊特製袋偷遍20市UNIQLO<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181116/large/a1605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181116%2Flarge%2Fa1605a.gif&h=dbd12881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鴛鴦大盜用特製手袋行竊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地一對90後「鴛鴦大盜」發現服裝品牌UNIQLO（內地稱優衣庫）有保安漏洞，於是自製一個令防盜磁扣失效的手袋，從南到北偷遍大半個中國UNIQLO門市，無一失手，他們還透過網絡直播銷贓，賺旅費遊山玩水。不過上得山多終遇虎，兩人在蘇州犯案時，被警方抓個正着，目前以涉嫌盜竊罪被刑拘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直播賣贓物賺旅費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181116/large/a1605b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181116%2Flarge%2Fa1605b.gif&h=555e2f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUNIQLO在中國設600多家門市。<br />\n<br />\n吳中區警方接報指，UNIQLO有衣服不翼而飛，警方翻查閉路電視發現，兩人在多家UNIQLO瘋狂行竊，最終在揚州拘捕這對鴛鴦大盜。姓王疑犯供稱，發現UNIQLO防盜措施薄弱，基本上只有衣服的防盜磁扣，公司為節省成本，店員數量遠不及一般商店，加上貨量大，商店職員即便發覺衣物被偷，寧願逃避責任，將其當成日常損耗而不報警。<br />\n<br />\n王男後與女友網購隔磁布，縫在一個手袋內層，讓磁扣通過防盜門時不報警。今年年初，兩人從河南出發巡偷之旅，經西安、重慶、貴陽、深圳，橫掃20多個省市的門市。兩人邊偷邊玩，為盡快套現，又以正價三折價錢放售，並以網上直播兜售，半年來完成160多單交易，最終在蘇州落網。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇《現代快報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n俄驚現「鯨魚監獄」疑轉售華水族館"},{"pid":"c513c770b14ab065e85ed6d2c7f58b22e517ef73","tid":904358,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"U記都要偷？"},{"pid":"fb377737c1a286f01ee3100986f2e3b76d223c6b","tid":904358,"uid":193364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他們還透過網絡直播銷贓，賺旅費遊山玩水</span><br />\n<br />\n真係得終國人先會咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990037614d8c05476aa89e2b14b29b331c6cfaa5","tid":904358,"uid":52087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fb377737c1a286f01ee3100986f2e3b76d223c6b","tid":904358,"uid":193364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他們還透過網絡直播銷贓，賺旅費遊山玩水</span><br />\n<br />\n真係得終國人先會咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"佢地唔撚搞到咁揚上網直播<br />\n就咁陰啲陰啲放左啲老鼠貨<br />\n<br />\n根本都未必會比人拉"},{"pid":"c29cbd52a3b57bc76e7a8f8edcba382744dbf58b","tid":904358,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c513c770b14ab065e85ed6d2c7f58b22e517ef73","tid":904358,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"U記都要偷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo 先有機會偷者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}